title: Wall Street ends down
text:
Wall Street ends down   01:08 
U.S. stocks closed lower in an up-and-down session, dragged down by tech and energy shares, as investors adjusted to a more volatile market. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
